</section>

{# ── EXPERT REVIEW · firm-level, no founder name. trust-row credential cells.
     (H2: Reviewed by the TechBrot Certified ProAdvisor team.) ── #}
<section class="sec reveal" id="ny-statenisland-review">
  <div class="ct read">
    <div class="idx"><span class="idx__n">§</span><span class="idx__t">Page review &amp; standards</span><span class="idx__rule"></span></div>
    <h2 class="h2" style="margin-bottom:24px;">Reviewed by the TechBrot Certified ProAdvisor team.</h2>
    <div class="prose">
      <p>Reviewed and maintained by the accounting team at <strong>TechBrot Inc.</strong>, an independent Certified QuickBooks ProAdvisor firm serving Staten Island and the wider New York City market. Staten Island tax figures &mdash; 8.875% combined sales tax; 4% UBT after the $95,000 gross-income threshold, with a credit fully offsetting UBT of $3,400 or less; and no Commercial Rent Tax, which applies only to Manhattan south of 96th Street &mdash; reflect <a href="https://www.nyc.gov/site/finance/index.page" rel="noopener nofollow">NYC Department of Finance</a> and <a href="https://www.tax.ny.gov/" rel="noopener nofollow">NY DTF</a> rules current as of the date below and are reviewed periodically. TechBrot provides bookkeeping and coordinates with your CPA, who files.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="trust-row">
      {%- for c in reviewCreds %}
      <div class="trust-row__item"><p class="trust-row__value" style="font-size:15px;">{{ c.label }}</p><p class="trust-row__label">{{ c.detail | safe }}</p></div>
      {%- if not loop.last %}<div class="trust-row__divider"></div>{%- endif %}
      {%- endfor %}
    </div>
    <p class="meta-reviewed"><span>Published: 2026-06-07</span><span>Updated: 2026-06-07</span><span>Reviewed: 2026-06-07 &middot; Certified QuickBooks ProAdvisor</span></p>
